@TaskTracker.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5227

### Get all tasks
GET {{TaskTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single task by ID
GET {{TaskTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new task
POST {{TaskTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first task",
  "description": "Optional description here",
  "status": 0,
  "dueDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Update an existing task
PUT {{TaskTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated task title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": 1,
  "dueDate": "2026-06-15T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Delete a task
DELETE {{TaskTracker.Api_HostAddress}}/tasks/1

###